claim.claim-text:
A heating cooker, comprising:
a main body constituting an outer wall;
a top plate, on which a cooking container is placed, and which is provided on a top side of the main body;
a coil base disposed below the top plate; and
a deformed-ring-shaped heating coil arranged on the coil base, wherein
a peripheral wall surface of the heating coil is formed to be perpendicular to an arrangement surface of the coil base.
